test_all_one_range:
assert [3, 5, 7] == [1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, ...]
  At index 0 diff: 3 != 1
  Right contains 4 more items, first extra item: 1
  Full diff:
  - [1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1]
  + [3, 5, 7]
test_even_range:
assert [1, 3, 5, 7] == []
  Left contains 4 more items, first extra item: 1
  Full diff:
  - []
  + [1, 3, 5, 7]
